				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText"> Another brilliant move by Sony<a name="54208"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jul 28 04 11:24 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span> Some time ago Sony added a higher xp mod to MM Castle. In fact when you ding 20 a window pops up suggesting you try MM castle for xp. Obviously trying to get some use out of this zone. I went there with an alt I'm leveling up and sure enough the xp is VERY good. All of this is fine...... until......
<br />

<br />
 They revamp Veeshan's Peak and added new quests. So how do you get VP faction up? You guessed it, in MM Castle. Now if you go to MMC it is filled with high level guilds killing everything in sight for VP faction. WTF? Seeing as they revamped VP anyway couldn't they have put the quests on a different faction or even added VP faction to another zone, maybe one that is old and unused.
<br />

<br />
 I just don't get it they make a nice xp zone much like PC and then they screw the whole thing up. Btw this is in no way a shot at the high level people working faction there. You need faction what else are you supposed to do. I made a comment in ooc about this while I was there and I apparently offended someone working faction there. He told me to go to Split Paw, I was just pointing out how stupid sony can be sheesh.</span></td>
